{
  "stem": "11723.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my mother didn't even know there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, uh, so I said to her, um, I am going to go through the Stalin statue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Uh, there was, um, a big, um-- um-- what-- something like Place de la Concorde.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it had-- originally, it had monuments to the, uh, tribes of Hungary who came in-- in 896, each of them on a horse or whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And, uh, on one side, there was a church, which they destroyed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in the place of it, they erected an enormous statue of Stalin-- our great father Stalin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was a-- a bronze statue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I heard that they were going to take that down, because that was the symbol of oppression.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, um, so I said to my sister, uh, come, let's go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We're going to go down-- this was at the end of that boulevard, the Andrassy Boulevard, which was the Champs-Elysees-type boulevard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it ended up like in the Place de la Concorde.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Similarities were obvious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Uh, the city planner had the same thing in mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Anyway, so we walked the length of that, uh, boulevard, which is maybe a mile and a half.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And by the time we got there, the crowds were enormous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And everybody's screaming and yelling and-- and there was just such electricity in the crowd.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was one of the most exhilarating moments in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they were trying to, uh, get the statue down with torches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Finally, they had to dynamite it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And, uh, the noise was just so deafening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the crowds were like-- like waves, you know, like in an ocean, the wave hits you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And everybody is kind of getting hurled forward.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
